{"id": 652, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对象做什么会让你感到情感幻灭？", "description": "恋爱时为我心跳停止，同居后嫌我拉屎费纸。", "record_count": 11706, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194640iM4av0wR7QTW5AuG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-28T11:25:13Z", "options": [{"id": 29952, "content": "貌合神离", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 332150}, {"id": 30208, "content": "一月联系一次，一次就要约炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334090}, {"id": 29441, "content": "挑食，只有两种东西不吃：这也不吃，那也不吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288}, {"id": 29697, "content": "对方让我吃屎去。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331830}, {"id": 29442, "content": "生活并不是很优越，却总找我要买高档奢侈品", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229892}, {"id": 29700, "content": "整天打游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298988}, {"id": 29956, "content": "一杯二锅头 呛得眼泪流", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211738NnMQG75bOu6Btwe3.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280137}, {"id": 44548, "content": "对于我内心坚持的事情从来没有理解过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290302}, {"id": 29446, "content": "没有对象的表示不会做这道题?", "image": null, "praise_count": 277, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232958}, {"id": 30470, "content": "发现穷的给嫌弃，话题无聊且无力吐槽，生活慢慢淡出。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265809}, {"id": 29447, "content": "矫情，却装出高冷的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181534}, {"id": 31751, "content": "大半年了还没合照", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340293}, {"id": 32775, "content": "生活这家伙没给我机会感情破灭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346428}, {"id": 29449, "content": "一个字，懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 370, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268556}, {"id": 30474, "content": "发现原来觉得无所谓的缺点变得不可忍受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334882}, {"id": 29707, "content": "看了以上回复，醉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 247574}, {"id": 29452, "content": "不愿意为我花钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330432}, {"id": 29708, "content": "忽略", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331860}, {"id": 29964, "content": "当我在这里把评论都看完的时候，我的爱情已经破灭了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291903}, {"id": 30476, "content": "对你许下超级多的承诺", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144822CpRfXc9INxTdjm1i.jpg", "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334885}, {"id": 29453, "content": "不愿意为我花钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 283, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330432}, {"id": 29965, "content": "我们是同居开始的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 332193}, {"id": 30221, "content": "不上进只会抖机灵还觉得自己聪明极了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244570}, {"id": 30477, "content": "没安全感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172472}, {"id": 39182, "content": "说着爱我，实际上互动变少了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 405663}, {"id": 29455, "content": "和别的女人聊天被发现，来一句我只是聊聊，又没发生什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 321, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325422}, {"id": 29967, "content": "行为幼稚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240749}, {"id": 30223, "content": "在一起后才知道他晚上睡觉前不！刷！牙！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324629}, {"id": 29456, "content": "我和他妈讨论一件事的决定时他选择沉默。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325422}, {"id": 29968, "content": "上厕所不冲，房间不收拾，衣服不整理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 122938}, {"id": 30736, "content": "我很困了还想啪啪啪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335768}, {"id": 29457, "content": "一点都不大度 斤斤计较...", "image": null, "praise_count": 156, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188501}, {"id": 30737, "content": "一吵架就要我回娘家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335768}, {"id": 29458, "content": "推卸责任", "image": null, "praise_count": 396, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325422}, {"id": 29714, "content": "“行了行了，是我错了还不行么”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256195}, {"id": 30482, "content": "不尊重", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197884}, {"id": 29459, "content": "对象是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325422}, {"id": 29715, "content": "呼噜声震天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313999}, {"id": 30995, "content": "做任何事情不跟我商量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336507}, {"id": 29717, "content": "我生日时对方觉得没什么 我更气", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306089}, {"id": 29462, "content": "对我有太多的脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 232, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330359}, {"id": 31767, "content": "拉低我的智商", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203001}, {"id": 29464, "content": "每天持续传递负能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 787, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304619}, {"id": 29721, "content": "做爱时越来越满足不了我，说他累", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331895}, {"id": 29466, "content": "持保留出厂意见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208981}, {"id": 29978, "content": "朝我发火，一点都受不了，而且太有攻击性了。希望永远不要。他眼睛瞪起来的样子实在太丑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333372}, {"id": 30490, "content": "两人相处遇到问题时沉默不语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163303}, {"id": 74779, "content": "和异性有暧昧关系?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598722}, {"id": 29723, "content": "唠叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255022}, {"id": 29468, "content": "总是对我不满，每夜好几次", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330613}]}